msg":"睇reddit講呢舊野應該上萬年前已經一早發生，所以到依家先響地球觀察到，同某d科幻小說情節一樣，地球人觀察到滅世太空災難已經太遲，最後毀滅得不明不白<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621595250882e07c7574559bd4fb9f8ec17b6fe3","tid":1164581,"uid":12609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:22:23.000Z","msg":"SOURCE <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"661b9cf22e8db74f92c667d906dd435191b5e62d","tid":1164581,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:28:14.000Z","msg":"天元突破"},{"pid":"5380802230c9cc4f1c49b23d49aeb675baa0d54e","tid":1164581,"uid":86272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb069c511fbca965cd180794aa0f1cb31212438c","tid":1164581,"uid":19527,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"8533c1dcabe16f8c3c9a4c97d46c4ff2ae895edd","tid":1164581,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:07:31.000Z","msg":"有乜概念股可炒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:08:11.000Z","msg":"彗星科技"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:28:59.000Z","msg":"笑左"},{"pid":"963ee972b29707fa9e0a09312d01baf4167ac26e","tid":1164581,"uid":69707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:31:16.000Z","msg":"焦土派出招"},{"pid":"6caa6259ceca447916ee86c5718468273362fcff","tid":1164581,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/marveldatabase/images/1/1b/Robert_Reynolds_%28Earth-616%29_from_Iron_Man_Vol_4_10_001.jpg/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/250?cb=20171223053008\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fmarveldatabase%2Fimages%2F1%2F1b%2FRobert_Reynolds_%2528Earth-616%2529_from_Iron_Man_Vol_4_10_001.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fscale-to-width-down%2F250%3Fcb%3D20171223053008&h=c0d41f70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e999d736d0faf6c